data.title: The Collected Works of John Stuart Mill, Volume VI - Essays on England, Ireland, and the Empire
data.meta_description: Vol. 6 of the 33 vol. Collected Works contains a number of Mill’s essays on contemporary political issues, including his essay Reorganization of the Reform Party.
